data.description:
Nestled on a picturesque street, 723 Old Savannah Dr stands as an exquisite embodiment of refined living and timeless elegance. This luxurious residence beckons with its sophisticated design, impeccable craftsmanship, and a plethora of desirable features, making it an irresistible prospect for those seeking an exceptional home.

As you approach the property, the  exterior facade, adorned with classic architectural details and tasteful landscaping, exudes a sense of stately charm.

Upon entering the home, you are greeted by a cozy foyer. The layout seamlessly balances open spaces with intimate corners, creating an atmosphere of comfort and luxury. New waterproof laminate extends through the living areas, dining room, office, bar, and kitchen and comes with a lifetime warranty.

The heart of the home is undoubtedly the gourmet chef's kitchen, a masterpiece of design and functionality. Equipped with modern appliances, sleek cabinetry, and a center island, this kitchen is a haven for culinary enthusiasts and a focal point for gatherings.

Entertainment possibilities abound, thanks to the gracious living and dining areas that flow seamlessly from room to room. The formal dining room, with its  stylish wainscoting, provides a captivating setting for hosting memorable dinner parties.

For quieter moments, the home offers a cozy office with built-in bookshelves and desk, a serene oasis where you can escape into your favorite literature. The main bedroom suite is a true retreat, boasting a spacious layout, a lavish en-suite bathroom with a standalone soaking tub, walk-in shower and a generous walk-in closet. All of the spacious bedrooms have been professionally mudded and painted to give this home's new owners a fresh start.

The allure extends outdoors, where the meticulously landscaped backyard beckons with a spacious patio, perfect for weekend cookouts or evening relaxation. Brand new gutters ensure proper drainage from this home during the rainy season, and you can rest easy knowing the roof and HVAC systems were recently replaced in 2021.

Elegance and comfort converge effortlessly in this desirable home, evident in every meticulously chosen detail, from the brand new crown moldings and baseboards to the modern finishes.
